      "content": "i mean i get that, but i've read online that they work on different pathways in the brain so they shouldn't really clash? like melatonin is just a hormone and ambien is a sedative. i'm just really desperate because i've only been getting like 3 hours of sleep and i can't function at work. wouldn't it be fine just to take a small dose of melatonin alongside it to help the transition?",
